{"tid":35624,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人識解夢？","createTime":"2016-12-12T08:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T10:03:11.000Z","uid":5424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ef594c4fbd6ecbc8c17ddb7069d6a6b243e2b85","tid":35624,"uid":5424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:05:12.000Z","msg":"記得喺高登有個解夢post<br />\n個巴打有冇黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80257a99df457805ac3fe7646208296bda65b0f2","tid":35624,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:05:34.000Z","msg":"我識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"000d0e6abc09bf740815a85eed5efe834f371666","tid":35624,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:06:51.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"28aa8bbfce45aeb6c87e71e48d66d92329ecd43d","tid":35624,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:08:17.000Z","msg":"自己google &quot;dream interpretation&quot;"},{"pid":"eceda5c8a005d5a502b687eaeb6cb2482d654dd7","tid":35624,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:03:11.000Z","msg":"識識地，但真心好花時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n解一個夢之前首先要了解一個人既背景<br />\n因為唔同背景既解法將會完全唔一樣<br />\n<br />\n簡單例子，夢見玩具<br />\n可能一般係同 兒時回憶，童年，小朋友，開心 等等有關<br />\n但原來你既工作正正係玩具店店員<br />\n咁呢樣野好可能就會變成壓力<br />\n<br />\n所以煩就煩在<br />\n幾乎每一樣野，每個人既解釋都差唔多<br />\n被追趕大致上都係同壓力有關<br />\n但某一啲關鍵既事件，可能係引致係夢中想法既來源<br />\n而呢啲想法係關鍵，但關鍵又未必只有一個<br />\n由童年，到學校生活，到家庭，到朋友，工作，好多觀念野都會有所影響<br />\n<br />\n解一個夢可以解成晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}